'''溴化镁'''，化学式MgBr<sub>2</sub>，是由[[溴|溴]]和[[镁|镁]]组成的白色或无色易潮解物质。通常在治疗[[神经紊乱|神经紊乱]]中用作[[镇静|镇静]]剂或抗[[痉挛|痉挛]]药物。<ref>Pradyot Patnaik. ''Handbook of Inorganic Chemicals''. McGraw-Hill, 2002, ISBN 0070494398</ref> 溴化镁溶于水，部分溶于[[乙醇|乙醇]]。在[[水氯镁石|水氯镁石]]或[[光卤石|光卤石]]中存在少量。亦可在某些海水、湖水（如[[死海|死海]]水）中找到。<ref name="ReferenceA">Gruyter, W. Conise Encyclopedia Chemistry, Walter de Gruyter & Company: Berlin, 1993; 612</ref><ref name=l>Lewis, R. J. Hawley’s Condensed Chemical Dictionary, 15th ed.; John Wiley &Sons Inc.:New York, 2007; 777</ref>

==制备==
溴化镁可由[[氢溴酸|氢溴酸]]和[[氢氧化镁|氢氧化镁]]反应后结晶得到。<ref name=l/>

:Mg(OH)<sub>2</sub> + 2 HBr → MgBr<sub>2</sub> + 2H<sub>2</sub>O

也可用[[氢溴酸|氢溴酸]]和[[碳酸镁|碳酸镁]]反应后蒸干，收集其固体得到。<ref name="ReferenceA"/>

另一种制备方法是将金属[[镁|镁]]加入[[液氨|液氨]]和[[溴化钠|溴化钠]]的溶液中制备。蒸发溶剂液氨，收集沉淀物即为溴化镁。<ref>Jacobson, C.A. Encyclopedia of Cemical Reactions, Reinhold Publishing Corporation: New York, 1951; 409</ref>

==用途==
溴化镁可以用作多种反应的[[催化剂|催化剂]]，如可加入溶剂或用于制备[[格氏试剂|格氏试剂]]。作溶剂可制在药学中应用广泛的[[二氢嘧啶|二氢嘧啶]]。二氢嘧啶在医药中可用于阻止钙通过通道，也可作为HIVgp-120-CD4抑制剂。<ref>{{cite journal|doi=10.1081/SCC-120027250|title=A Facile and Efficient One‐Pot Synthesis of Dihydropyrimidinones Catalyzed by Magnesium Bromide Under Solvent‐Free Conditions|year=2004|last1=Salehi|first1=Hojatollah|last2=Guo|first2=Qing‐Xiang|journal=Synthetic Communications|volume=34|pages=171 }}</ref> 

溴化镁也可作为[[安定剂|安定剂]]。<ref name="ReferenceA"/> 溴化镁与[[二氯甲烷|二氯甲烷]]一起作催化剂可使[[烯烃|烯烃]][[氢化|氢化]]过程中产生特殊的[[对称性|对称性]]和[[手性|手性]]。<ref>{{cite journal|doi=10.1021/ol020032m|title=Magnesium Bromide Mediated Highly Diastereoselective Heterogeneous Hydrogenation of Olefins|year=2002|last1=Bouzide|first1=Abderrahim|journal=Organic Letters|volume=4|pages=1347|pmid=11950359|issue=8}}</ref> 

溴化镁与其他[[官能团|官能团]]结合时可发挥更大的催化作用。与[[乙基|乙基]]相连可用于[[三酸甘油酯|三酸甘油酯]]的区域性分析。<ref>Ando, Y; Tomita, Y; Haba, Y. [http://www.jstage.jst.go.jp/article/jos/57/8/57_459/_article Preparation of Ethyl Magnesium Bromide for Regiospecific Analysis of Triacylglycerols] Journal of Oleo Science, 2008, 57, 459</ref> 

六水合溴化镁可作为[[阻燃剂|阻燃剂]]。用0.125 mol/L 的六水合溴化镁加入至[[棉花|棉花]]中可起到阻燃的作用。<ref>{{cite journal|doi=10.1007/s10973-007-8928-4|title=XRD characterization of the ashes from a burned cellulosic fabric impregnated with magnesium bromide hexahydrate as flame-retardant|year=2008|last1=Mostashari|first1=S. M.|last2=Fayyaz|first2=F.|journal=Journal of Thermal Analysis and Calorimetry|volume=92|pages=845}}</ref> 

溴化镁被用于合成第一种稳定的含镁[[类硅烯|类硅烯]]（即通式为 R<sub>2</sub>SiM<sub>X</sub> 的物质，其中M为金属原子， R为烃基）。传统上类硅烯中的金属原子只可用[[锂|锂]]、[[钠|钠]]、[[钾|钾]]。<ref>{{cite journal|doi=10.1021/om060589w|title=A Stable Magnesium Bromosilylenoid: Transmetalation of a Lithium Bromosilylenoid by Magnesium Bromide|year=2006|last1=Lim|first1=Young Mook|last2=Cho|first2=Hyeon Mo|last3=Lee|first3=Myong Euy|last4=Baeck|first4=Kyoung  Koo|journal=Organometallics|volume=25|pages=4960}}</ref>

